Package: maputils
Version: 0.2.0
Title: SNAP-Specific Leaflet Utilities and Maps Collection for Shiny Apps
Description: Common utility functions and polygon maps used across multiple Shiny apps
    specific to a SNAP context, like the snaputils package but separate and also specific to Leaflet maps. 
    This package inherents from the apputils package and is a satellite member of the SNAPverse collection of R packages.
Authors@R: c(person("Matthew", "Leonawicz", email = "mfleonawicz@alaska.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
